OL,3,C'Martha' in Baby Reindeer sues Netflix
OL,4,Cfor $170 million
OL,6,FA woman claiming to be the inspiration
OL,7,Ffor the character Maratha in Richard
OL,8,FGadd's hit TV series Baby Reindeer is
OL,9,Fsuing Netflix for at least $170
OL,10,Fmillion (#133 million).
OL,12,FFiona Harvey has accused the streaming
OL,13,Fplatform of defamation, intentional
OL,14,Finfliction of emotional distress,
OL,15,Fnegligence, gross negligence, and
OL,16,Fviolations of her right of publicity
OL,17,Fin the lawsuit filed at the
OL,18,FCalifornian federal court.
