OL,3,C'Martha' in Baby Reindeer sues Netflix
OL,4,Cfor $170 million
OL,6,FIt comes after she claimed to be the
OL,7,Finspiration behind the character of
OL,8,FMartha Scott, who stalks Gadd's
OL,9,Fcharacter Donny Dunn after he serves
OL,10,Fher a free cup of tea in the pub where
OL,11,Fhe works.
OL,13,FThe show is said to be based on the
OL,14,Freal-life experiences of comedian and
OL,15,Fwriter Gadd. After the show aired, he
OL,16,Fasked viewers not to speculate over
OL,17,Fthe real people who inspired the
OL,18,Fseries.
