OL,3,C'Martha' in Baby Reindeer sues Netflix
OL,4,Cfor $170 million
OL,6,FIn the new lawsuit, Harvey has accused
OL,7,FNetflix of spreading "brutal lies",
OL,8,Fincluding that she is a "twice
OL,9,Fconvicted stalker who was sentenced to
OL,10,Ffive years in prison".
OL,12,F"Defendants told these lies, and never
OL,13,Fstopped, because it was a better story
OL,14,Fthan the truth, and better stories
OL,15,Fmade money," it states.
OL,17,F"As a result of defendants' lies,
OL,18,Fmalfeasance and utterly reckless
OL,19,Fmisconduct, Harvey's life had been
OL,20,Fruined."
