OL,3,C'Martha' in Baby Reindeer sues Netflix
OL,4,Cfor $170 million
OL,6,FThe court documents allege Netflix
OL,7,F"did literally nothing" to confirm
OL,8,Fthat the story represented was true,
OL,9,Fstating that "Harvey has never been
OL,10,Fconvicted of any crime and has never
OL,11,Fbeen to prison".
OL,13,FA statement from Netflix said: "We
OL,14,Fintend to defend this matter
OL,15,Fvigorously and to stand by Richard
OL,16,FGadd's right to tell his story."
